      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, super clean inside and out, and runs like a dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Drop me a message if you want to come see it\u2014I\u2019d love to show you around!",
      "price": 33000.0,
