    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 981-generation Cayman S features the highly coveted 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine, delivering 325 horsepower with a linear torque curve and an evocative exhaust note. Equipped with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a mid-engine layout, the vehicle offers exceptional polar moment of inertia and precise turn-in. The chassis is enhanced with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for adaptive damping and a mechanical limited-slip differential that ensures optimal power delivery through the apex. Recent service includes a full cooling system pressure test and new spark plugs to ensure the high-revving powertrain remains within factory tolerances. While the finish reflects its status as a dedicated driver's tool, the synchromesh is smooth, and the steering rack remains communicative and tight.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
